description:
Hrithik wakes up from a bad dream and is asked by his Tanvi as to what did he dream about. Elsewhere, Yamini asks her husband to take off his black suit and then he is asked by his niece to come soon for the prayer service. On the other hand, a pandit tells Yamini that her son needs to get married before the age of 25 or otherwise his life will be in trouble. Later, Hrithik hits an old man with his car and decides to take him to the hospital. In the meantime, Hrithik and his relatives joke around about ghosts being in the haveli but Yamini interrupts their conversation. Stay tuned to know catch all the excitement.
